description: For sale: $169,900. Check out this unique charmer! Great home with 4 bedrooms, it's move-in ready and affordable-a rare find! With a large yard and located on a quiet street near the heart of Faribault, this home has many features beginning on the outside but continuing throughout the 2000+ finished square feet inside. With the garage in the back of the home, the back entrance is likely to become the most used, & it is set up with a practical porch/mud room area that enters into the kitchen. The rest of the main level features a cute kitchen, 2 bedrooms, a full bath right off the master bedroom, separate dining & living room, and a bonus hobby room/storage/office area, too! Upstairs you will find 2 more bedrooms and a 3/4 bathroom, plus a nice getting ready/closet area with a separate outdoor entrance- the home used to be a duplex and this area was the upstairs kitchen. This home has so much space & numerous unique features-use your imagination to design a home perfect for your needs & hobbies!

Open, multi-level plan offers views yet max privacy! New master ensuite! New Timberline shingles!  New ceramic wood plank tile on main floor! Whirlpool frig with lower freezer & ice-maker! GE microwave! New mud room w/ sink & 2nd frig! 2-car garage & concrete driveway! Master includes sliding deck door, jetted tub, heated floors, tiled bath & walk-in closet!  One bedroom & bath on main entry level! 3rd bedroom located on private upper level has sliding door, balcony & amazing lake vistas! Natural gas furnace recently serviced! Newer, tankless gas water heater. 150AMP electric. Reverse osmosis water softener! Most major items already updated -- bring your finishing touches! Private paved road! Northfield 659 schools.

For sale: $272,000. Beautifully updated home on a secluded east side cul-de-sac. Open concept floor plan with a remodeled kitchen, center island bar, granite counters and double ovens. There are gleaming hardwood floors, a large pantry and custom maple cabinets with multiple pull out slide shelves. The main floor family room has a vaulted ceiling, skylights, a gas fireplace and an amazing view of the private backyard. The lovely deck is perfect for hosting summer BBQs or just sipping your morning coffee and enjoying the abundant wildlife, lovely landscaping and mature trees. The second family room is located on the lower level and has large windows and lots of natural light. With a fireplace and wet bar, your family and friends can enjoy shooting pool, watching a ball game or just hanging out. The over-sized, heated garage has a separate heated workshop and lots of storage. This home is located close to Shattuck Saint Mary's and the Minnesota State Academy for the Deaf.

Also, upon entering is one of two gathering rooms on the main floor, this one flows right into the dining room and provides plenty of space to entertain guests.  You will be impressed with the large kitchen off the dining with updated appliances and plenty of space.   As you go through the kitchen towards the back of the home you will be delighted to find a mud room along with an additional cozy family room perfect for relaxing.  The beauty of this home continues on the upper level with 2 bedrooms, a large 'dressing'? area, walk in closet and updated ? bath.  This home sits on a large lot with a 1 stall garage   carport  and is the one you will want to call home!

Nice spot in Cannon City with a quickdrive to Northfield and Faribault schools. Call to see and get ready to S-T-R-E-T-C-H O-U-T! Video walk through available, just ask for link!

description: Recently sold: $195,000. THAT COUNTRY FEELING! If you're craving that country feeling, but you'd rather be in town, you're in luck! This beautiful 3BR/2BA rambler is located on the edge of town on an extra large 0.34-acre lot. The ranch-style home has been one of the most popular, sought-after architectural styles for decades, offering simplicity, practicality, & long-term livability. Curved arched doorways & a charming built-in corner hutch. Super-large kitchen with coffee bar & dining area. Fantastic drop-zone area combined with a spacious pantry. Hang out in the cozy living room or the lower level family room. Super large backyard with patio, fire pit, & garden shed. The backyard is fenced-in, but the property line extends well beyond the back fence! Oversized 2-stall attached garage with workshop area. You will love the parking pad for additional vehicles! For peace of mind, there's a water drainage system in the basement. Explore the nature trails located out your back door. The perfect home!
